<br>
I gotten to the part where im started to forage the items needed for our epic.<br>
<br>
My forage skill is 130 and im level 53 (If thats matter)<br>
<br>
Yesterday i was standing in misty for 5 hours and pressing forage button every time i could. I got alot of stuff but no sweetened Mudroot. Sigh<br>
<br>
My question is: Is there places in the zones there is a better chance of getting these items or is it purely chance?<br>
<br>
How long did other ppl spent on their forage part? <p><hr><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" color=#5c7898>
<select size="1">
