<br>
GFay - I found the Ripened Heartfruit before I started my epic, and left it in the bank.<br>
Everfrost - I spent 3 hours of foraging, I bound myself outside Perma and fought IGs.<br>
Misty - Urk, this one took 4 hours.  I rearranged my spellbook.<br>
Innothule - This took about an hour and a half.<br>
FV - 20 minutes<br>
<br>
In Everfrost, I found my root as I was walking to give a fellow IG killer a spell.  In Innothule, I found the mushroom after helping a little enchanter kill some shadowed men for a while.  There were no similar karmic events in GFay, Misty or FV, but I thought it was a funny coincidence in the other two zones.<br>
<br>
